{
  "survey": {
    "type": "survey",
    "id": "survey_ai_design_tool_demo_20260423",
    "title": "<h1>AI + 设计工具需求调研 Demo</h1>",
    "description": "<p>这是一份用于 <strong>survey-creator-skill</strong> 开源示例的综合问卷，用来演示 <em>schema → validation → HTML</em> 的完整流程。</p><p>本示例同时覆盖：<strong>logic</strong>、<strong>Pagination 手动分页</strong>、<strong>一页多题</strong>、<strong>child input</strong>、<strong>score</strong> 与 <strong>nps</strong>。</p>",
    "attribute": {
      "onePageOneQuestion": false,
      "allowBack": false,
      "media": []
    }
  },
  "questions": [
    {
      "type": "radio",
      "id": "question_recent_usage",
      "title": "<h2>过去 3 个月，你是否使用过 AI 工具来输出 UI 稿？</h2>",
      "description": "<p>这里会触发后续逻辑：若你选“高频使用”，会显示进阶追问；若你选“还没有正式使用过”，会直接跳过中间页。</p>",
      "attribute": {
        "required": true,
        "random": true,
        "media": []
      },
      "option": [
        {
          "id": "option_used_often",
          "title": "<p>是，已经高频使用</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "random": false,
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_used_tried",
          "title": "<p>试过，但还没形成稳定工作流</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_not_used",
          "title": "<p>还没有正式使用过</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_other_state",
          "title": "<p>其他，请说明</p>",
          "child": [
            {
              "type": "input",
              "id": "child_other_state_reason",
              "title": "<p>请简单描述你的现状</p>",
              "attribute": {
                "required": false,
                "dataType": "text",
                "placeholder": "例如：只在灵感探索阶段使用，还没有进入正式项目",
                "maxLength": 160
              }
            }
          ],
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "question_feature_priority",
      "title": "<h2>如果要选一个 AI 设计工具，你最在意哪些能力？</h2>",
      "description": "<p>这是第一页中的第二道题，用来演示一页多题。这里也会触发 <code>auto_select_option</code> 和 <code>hide_option</code>。</p>",
      "attribute": {
        "required": true,
        "random": true,
        "media": []
      },
      "option": [
        {
          "id": "option_feature_prompt_to_ui",
          "title": "<p>一句话生成页面 / 线框 / 高保真 UI</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "random": false,
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_feature_design_system",
          "title": "<p>能复用设计系统与已有组件</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_feature_editability",
          "title": "<p>生成后还能继续编辑，而不是只能看图</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_feature_collaboration",
          "title": "<p>支持和 Figma / Pencil / Codex 等工作流协作</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_feature_blank_canvas",
          "title": "<p>我更希望从纯空白画布手工开始</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_feature_other",
          "title": "<p>其他能力诉求</p>",
          "child": [
            {
              "type": "input",
              "id": "child_feature_other_text",
              "title": "<p>请补充你的能力诉求</p>",
              "attribute": {
                "required": false,
                "dataType": "text",
                "placeholder": "例如：自动生成交互动效、自动补齐埋点、自动生成设计说明",
                "maxLength": 160
              }
            }
          ],
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_feature_not_sure",
          "title": "<p>暂无明确判断，以上都不确定</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "exclusive": true,
            "media": []
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Pagination",
      "id": "page_sep_logic_followup"
    },
    {
      "type": "input",
      "id": "question_workflow_bottleneck",
      "title": "<h2>如果你已经尝试过 AI 出图，目前最卡的环节是什么？</h2>",
      "description": "<p>这是第二页中的逻辑追问题，默认隐藏，仅在“高频使用”时展示；若用户从未使用过 AI，则整页会被跳过。</p>",
      "attribute": {
        "required": true,
        "media": []
      },
      "option": [
        {
          "id": "option_workflow_bottleneck_text",
          "title": "<p>请描述你最主要的工作流阻塞点</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "dataType": "text",
            "placeholder": "例如：生成结果不稳定、难以复用设计系统、改稿成本高",
            "maxLength": 200,
            "minLength": 4
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Pagination",
      "id": "page_sep_profile_and_eval"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "question_platform_focus",
      "title": "<h2>你目前主要面向哪些端进行设计？</h2>",
      "description": "<p>这里演示 <code>mutual-exclusion</code>：Web-first 与 Mobile-first 不能同时选中，但仍可与其他普通选项共存。</p>",
      "attribute": {
        "required": true,
        "random": false,
        "media": []
      },
      "option": [
        {
          "id": "option_platform_web_first",
          "title": "<p>Web-first</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "mutual-exclusion": true,
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_platform_mobile_first",
          "title": "<p>Mobile-first</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "mutual-exclusion": true,
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_platform_cross_platform",
          "title": "<p>跨端统一设计</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_platform_admin_b2b",
          "title": "<p>B 端后台 / 配置类系统</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "media": []
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "input",
      "id": "question_profile",
      "title": "<h2>为了更好理解你的背景，请补充以下信息</h2>",
      "description": "<p>该题演示一个 <strong>input</strong> 问题可同时包含多个字段，并按 <code>option[].id</code> 分别提交。</p>",
      "attribute": {
        "required": true,
        "media": []
      },
      "option": [
        {
          "id": "option_profile_role",
          "title": "<p>你的角色</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "dataType": "text",
            "placeholder": "例如：UI 设计师 / 产品经理 / 前端开发",
            "maxLength": 60,
            "minLength": 2
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_profile_email",
          "title": "<p>邮箱</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "dataType": "email",
            "placeholder": "name@example.com",
            "maxLength": 120
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_profile_team_size",
          "title": "<p>团队人数</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "dataType": "number",
            "placeholder": "例如：5",
            "maxLength": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "score",
      "id": "question_score_current_tools",
      "title": "<h2>请给你现在使用的设计工具组合打分</h2>",
      "description": "<p>1 分最低，5 分最高。</p>",
      "attribute": {
        "required": true,
        "media": []
      },
      "option": [
        {
          "id": "option_score_quality",
          "title": "<p>输出质量</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "scope": [
              1,
              5
            ],
            "step": 1,
            "scoreDesc": {
              "1": "很差",
              "2": "较差",
              "3": "一般",
              "4": "满意",
              "5": "非常满意"
            },
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_score_speed",
          "title": "<p>产出速度</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "scope": [
              1,
              5
            ],
            "step": 1,
            "scoreDesc": {
              "1": "很差",
              "2": "较差",
              "3": "一般",
              "4": "满意",
              "5": "非常满意"
            },
            "media": []
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "option_score_editability",
          "title": "<p>后续可编辑性</p>",
          "attribute": {
            "scope": [
              1,
              5
            ],
            "step": 1,
            "scoreDesc": {
              "1": "很差",
              "2": "较差",
              "3": "一般",
              "4": "满意",
              "5": "非常满意"
            },
            "media": []
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "nps",
      "id": "question_nps_recommendation",
      "title": "<h2>如果有一款真正可编辑、可复用设计系统、可直接进入工作流的 AI 设计工具，你愿意推荐给同事吗？</h2>",
      "description": "<p>请按 0-10 分打分，0 表示完全不愿意推荐，10 表示非常愿意推荐。</p>",
      "attribute": {
        "required": true,
        "media": []
      },
      "option": [
        {
          "id": "option_nps_recommendation",
          "attribute": {
            "scope": [
              0,
              10
            ],
            "media": [],
            "scoreDesc": {
              "0-6": "不推荐",
              "7-8": "中立",
              "9-10": "愿意推荐"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "finish": {
    "type": "finish",
    "id": "finish_ai_design_tool_demo",
    "title": "<h2>感谢你的反馈</h2>",
    "description": "<p>这份 demo 问卷已经覆盖了 <strong>radio / checkbox / input / score / nps / logic / Pagination</strong> 等主要能力。</p><p>提交后，页面会按默认 submission contract 组装 payload，并在浏览器中输出到 <code>console.log</code>。</p>",
    "media": []
  },
  "logic": [
    {
      "id": "logic_show_workflow_bottleneck",
      "when": {
        "questionId": "question_recent_usage",
        "operator": "selected",
        "optionId": "option_used_often"
      },
      "action": {
        "type": "show_question",
        "targetQuestionId": "question_workflow_bottleneck"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "logic_auto_select_prompt_to_ui",
      "when": {
        "questionId": "question_recent_usage",
        "operator": "selected",
        "optionId": "option_used_often"
      },
      "action": {
        "type": "auto_select_option",
        "targetQuestionId": "question_feature_priority",
        "targetOptionId": "option_feature_prompt_to_ui"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "logic_hide_blank_canvas_for_power_users",
      "when": {
        "questionId": "question_recent_usage",
        "operator": "selected",
        "optionId": "option_used_often"
      },
      "action": {
        "type": "hide_option",
        "targetQuestionId": "question_feature_priority",
        "targetOptionId": "option_feature_blank_canvas"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "logic_jump_skip_followup_page",
      "when": {
        "questionId": "question_recent_usage",
        "operator": "selected",
        "optionId": "option_not_used"
      },
      "action": {
        "type": "jump_to_page",
        "targetQuestionId": "question_platform_focus"
      }
    }
  ]
}